{"tid":2353793,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"武漢肺炎︱中學每日分兩節容許學生回校 校長同意稱安排彈性","createTime":"2021-01-05T04:28:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-05T07:15:15.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"38a25aea04f84a021e97e473b0c8ebf8a04f8b4a","tid":2353793,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T04:28:28.000Z","msg":"教育局局長楊潤雄昨日（4日）公佈，全港中、小學及幼稚園將繼續停止面授課堂至農曆新年假，而中、小學可繼續沿用舊有措施，安排部份或個別班級的學生回校。中學校長會主席連鎮邦今日在商台節目表示，教育局容許中學下周一起，每日安排上、下午兩節，按校本情況讓學生回校上課或考試，每節不得超過全校六分一人。連鎮邦稱措施回應到學界實際需要，能令校方更有彈性，相信學校陸續會在未來幾日公佈安排。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210105/KR4GVCV77JBAFJOOY6TQF6ED3I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210105%2FKR4GVCV77JBAFJOOY6TQF6ED3I%2F&d=zT4eWHrghymhx70gWSuuOcv4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=4c8c1382\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210105%2FKR4GVCV77JBAFJOOY6TQF6ED3I%2F&h=11765f1f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210105/KR4GVCV77JBAFJOOY6TQF6ED3I/</a>"},{"pid":"01e37a0262a09a76175bc4d3d7b5e5fe57144a73","tid":2353793,"uid":63909,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T05:05:23.000Z","msg":"ON L 7 9<br />\n記者會都怕開啦<br />\n返學唔多人過記者會<br />\n全無LOGIC"},{"pid":"c68cb3f1db516dfaf27c5a9706e8bb23a5f3389c","tid":2353793,"uid":257914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T05:39:09.000Z","msg":"係咪上晝放咗成間學校消毒一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a185925c01bdca0d4f78f10dc778e7ffc680c7df","tid":2353793,"uid":87735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T05:46:05.000Z","msg":"又要迫車迫巴士"},{"pid":"4316efc7de49d254f9c415cc7410674fa2f17844","tid":2353793,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c68cb3f1db516dfaf27c5a9706e8bb23a5f3389c","tid":2353793,"uid":257914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T05:3